{"tid":997551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［中國式陰道］加駐華大使發表奶共言論被革職","createTime":"2019-01-27T09:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T13:46:25.000Z","uid":99856,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"75829e76240758f954fde0dd68ce5743b6507410","tid":997551,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:12:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190127/59190262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190127%2F59190262&d=IaL90kcc6RX%2FizET26T3O%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9e4f4a87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190127%2F59190262&h=298d413f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190127/59190262</a><br />\n<br />\n【內容更新、新增動新聞】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【華為危機】加國撤換駐華大使 內地網民：只圖口快忘了身份<br />\n<br />\n加拿大駐華大使麥家廉(John McCallum)近日多次就華為副董事長孟晚舟引渡案發表敏感言論，終被加拿大總理杜魯多革職。<br />\n<br />\n杜魯多周六發表聲明說：「我昨晚已要求和接受加拿大駐華大使麥家廉的辭職。」他感謝麥家廉過去20年為公職服務，又指加拿大駐華大使館公使倪杰民(Jim Nickel)將會接替麥家廉，擔任代理大使。<br />\n<br />\n杜魯多沒有解釋革退麥家廉的原因，但麥家廉日前指孟晚舟有強力理據反對美國引渡要求，其後承認失言，杜魯多周四還表示無意撤換駐華大使。怎料麥家廉周五再公開評論孟晚舟案件，稱若美國放棄引渡是好事，令杜魯多無法再容忍。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">68歲的麥家廉本人與中國關係密切，近日他向華文傳媒表示，他的妻子林秀英（Nancy Lim）是馬來西亞華裔，三個兒子的妻子也都是華裔，分別出生於中國內地、香港和馬來西亞。</span></span>麥家廉2017年起擔任加拿大駐華大使，之前曾擔任加拿大國會下議院議員、國防部長、難民及公民部長等職務。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大在野保守黨領袖謝爾(Andrew Scheer)指摘，「數日前就應該炒掉」麥家廉，因為他的言論令孟晚舟案件更政治化，也損害加拿大聲譽，令外界以為加拿大想向北京傳遞訊息紓緩緊張關係。有前外交官亦批評麥家廉的言論令加拿大的立場不清，杜魯多把他革職，令北京明白麥家廉並不是代表加拿大發言。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"d92c692e171c84d908f7615f686dba75f01425c4","tid":997551,"uid":99856,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"支那式陰道影響力真係無遠弗屆"},{"pid":"cea429a2965cce89b5a5f64514a62a9ea96704ef","tid":997551,"uid":3302,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"成家都係拎華人黎做肉便器<br />\n唔怪得"},{"pid":"7eaf0fda7a04a4b7be41fae1977149492773dca6","tid":997551,"uid":49588,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"全家都比「中國陰道」攻陷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c896f6aca9eb0b1482bf9806674a48eb464e55","tid":997551,"uid":99856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7eaf0fda7a04a4b7be41fae1977149492773dca6","tid":997551,"uid":49588,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"全家都比「中國陰道」攻陷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"左癌仲未認識到支那做緊咩"},{"pid":"9f56f91720d775ede069715894f6ae43e7ff517a","tid":997551,"uid":163783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"分別出生於中國內地、香港和馬來西亞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57e4be80382ee7ec454458fdf4b44d9cc1b139c","tid":997551,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:19:36.000Z","msg":"中國式陰道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e992ffdb186782f72fd058edd3ceb9bcdcc41e1b","tid":997551,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:23:15.000Z","msg":"【華為孟晚舟被捕】被撤加駐華大使麥家廉　妻子與兒媳均為華裔<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/議事廳/288150/華為孟晚舟被捕-被撤加駐華大使麥家廉-妻子與兒媳均為華裔\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3%2F288150%2F%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%A2%AB%E6%92%A4%E5%8A%A0%E9%A7%90%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%BA%A5%E5%AE%B6%E5%BB%89-%E5%A6%BB%E5%AD%90%E8%88%87%E5%85%92%E5%AA%B3%E5%9D%87%E7%82%BA%E8%8F%